{"pageModel":{"attributes":{"id":"","name":"106109.dita","viewName":"DitaDetail"},"elements":{"ditaContent":{"name":"DITAContent","value":"<article id=\"getting-started-workflow\" class=\"topic concept\">\r\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Getting Started Workflow</h1>\r\n<div class=\"body conbody\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">Follow this workflow to get started with Security Cloud Control:</p>\r\n<ol class=\"ol\">\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">As an existing user of one of these Cisco security products, you received an\r\n                    email notifying you that your product subscription is being integrated with Security Cloud Control.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">Cisco security operations created a new Security Cloud Control organization for you and integrated your product with that organization.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">Now that the organization has been created, you can sign in to Security Cloud Control at  <a data-scope=\"external\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://security.cisco.com\" title=\"\">https://security.cisco.com</a>\r\n                    using your Security Cloud Sign On Account and you can add users to your organization. Those users can sign in to the organization with their Cisco Secure Sign On account or create a new account if they don't\r\n                    have one.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">Set your default landing page. </p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">Your organization was created in the computing region of your existing product. If you need to,\r\n                    you can create additional organizations. Be mindful of the preferred region you choose for those organizations, not every new product you subscribe to is available in every region.\r\n                    Consider the region in which you need your data to be stored.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">Add a domain to your organization.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">Integrate the identity provider with Secure Cloud Sign On.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">Add new users and create groups in your organization and assign them permissions to manage applications and services.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">Associate new products with your organization using new claim codes.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">Onboard firewalls and other devices to the Firewall application in Security Cloud Control.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li class=\"li\">\r\n<p class=\"p\">Continue with the next steps of configuring your organization.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</div>\r\n</article>\r\n","ditaVal":"","format":"html"},"bookTitle":{"value":""},"shortDescription":{"value":""}}},"parameters":{"appId":"SccPlatformGsgExisting","topicAlias":"gsg_exist_cust"}}